channel.title: Server Status checker - Working Online Demo - And download
channel.description:
Hey, I was searching through my webserver files on my pc when I found my old server status checker. Since I no longer make servers I am now giving it away.. You can test it online at my [url=http://doognotna.uk.to/status]WEBSITE[/url]. But since I used to sell copies of it, it has a "secure install system" so you need a username and password to install it. For a copy, add me on msn: megatony@orcon.net.nz
I will create you a password and username and give you the checker.
If you want, I will also give you some forums that I am going to start making in five mins.
xxlegitxx - were you the spammer? Cause you know I hate spam!
